---
// LPMoments.astro - "Moments That Hurt" section
---

<section class="moments">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Moments That Hurt</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      Every developer knows these feelings. Caro makes them disappear.
    </p>

    <div class="moments-grid">
      <!-- Moment 1: Did I type that right? -->
      <div class="moment-card">
        <div class="moment-before">
          <div class="moment-icon">ðŸ˜°</div>
          <h3 class="moment-pain">"Did I type that right?"</h3>
          <p class="moment-description">
            Staring at a command you found on Stack Overflow. Is that a backtick or a quote?
            Will this delete everything or just the logs?
          </p>
          <div class="moment-example bad">
            <code>rm -rf /var/log/*.log</code>
            <span class="doubt">...right?</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="moment-divider">
          <span class="with-caro">With Caro</span>
        </div>
        <div class="moment-after">
          <div class="moment-example good">
            <span class="caro-label">You say:</span>
            <span class="nl-input">"Delete old log files safely"</span>
          </div>
          <div class="moment-example validated">
            <span class="caro-label">Caro:</span>
            <code>find /var/log -name "*.log" -mtime +30 -delete</code>
            <span class="badge safe">âœ“ Safe</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Moment 2: What if this breaks prod? -->
      <div class="moment-card">
        <div class="moment-before">
          <div class="moment-icon">ðŸ’€</div>
          <h3 class="moment-pain">"What if this breaks prod?"</h3>
          <p class="moment-description">
            That sinking feeling before hitting Enter on a production server.
            No undo. No sandbox. Just raw fear.
          </p>
          <div class="moment-example bad">
            <code>chmod -R 777 /</code>
            <span class="doubt">copied from tutorial...</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="moment-divider">
          <span class="with-caro">With Caro</span>
        </div>
        <div class="moment-after">
          <div class="moment-example blocked">
            <span class="badge danger">â›” BLOCKED</span>
            <p class="warning-text">This command would make all system files world-writable. Suggested safe alternative:</p>
            <code>chmod 755 ./your-directory</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Moment 3: What runs on this machine? -->
      <div class="moment-card">
        <div class="moment-before">
          <div class="moment-icon">ðŸ¤”</div>
          <h3 class="moment-pain">"What runs on this machine?"</h3>
          <p class="moment-description">
            BSD? Linux? macOS? Is it GNU find or BSD find?
            Why does every server have different flags?
          </p>
          <div class="moment-example bad">
            <code>find . -regex ".*\.log" -print0</code>
            <span class="doubt">works on my mac but...</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="moment-divider">
          <span class="with-caro">With Caro</span>
        </div>
        <div class="moment-after">
          <div class="moment-example platform-aware">
            <span class="badge platform">Detected: Ubuntu 22.04</span>
            <p class="platform-text">Using GNU coreutils syntax:</p>
            <code>find . -regextype posix-extended -regex ".*\.log" -print0</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .moments {
    padding: 100px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0a0f 0%, #0f0f14 100%);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #888;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 60px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .moments-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .moment-card {
    background: #12121a;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid #1f1f2a;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .moment-card:hover {
    border-color: #333;
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .moment-before {
    padding: 28px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1a24 0%, #12121a 100%);
  }

  .moment-icon {
    font-size: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .moment-pain {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .moment-description {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #888;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .moment-example {
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Monaco', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .moment-example.bad {
    background: rgba(255, 85, 85, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 85, 85, 0.2);
  }

  .moment-example.bad code {
    color: #ff8888;
  }

  .moment-example .doubt {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #666;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
  }

  .moment-divider {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #ff6b35, transparent);
    height: 2px;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .with-caro {
    background: #0f0f14;
    color: #ff6b35;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    position: absolute;
  }

  .moment-after {
    padding: 28px;
    background: #0f0f14;
  }

  .moment-example.good,
  .moment-example.validated {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .moment-example.good {
    background: rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.2);
  }

  .moment-example.validated {
    background: rgba(80, 250, 123, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(80, 250, 123, 0.2);
  }

  .moment-example.validated code {
    color: #50fa7b;
    display: block;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .moment-example.blocked {
    background: rgba(255, 85, 85, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 85, 85, 0.2);
  }

  .moment-example.blocked code {
    color: #50fa7b;
    display: block;
    margin-top: 12px;
    background: rgba(80, 250, 123, 0.1);
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .moment-example.platform-aware {
    background: rgba(139, 233, 253, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(139, 233, 253, 0.2);
  }

  .moment-example.platform-aware code {
    color: #8be9fd;
    display: block;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .caro-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #666;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
  }

  .nl-input {
    color: #ff8c42;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
  }

  .badge.safe {
    background: rgba(80, 250, 123, 0.2);
    color: #50fa7b;
    margin-left: 8px;
  }

  .badge.danger {
    background: rgba(255, 85, 85, 0.2);
    color: #ff5555;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .badge.platform {
    background: rgba(139, 233, 253, 0.2);
    color: #8be9fd;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .warning-text, .platform-text {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #888;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    margin: 8px 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .moments-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .moments {
      padding: 60px 16px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .moment-before, .moment-after {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .moment-pain {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
